# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
# 
# 1. For Cloud Setup:
#    - Create a Supabase project at https://supabase.com
#    - Copy your project URL and anon key from Settings > API
#    - Set NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL and NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#    - Set USE_LOCAL_SUPABASE=false or leave it unset
#
# 2. For Local Setup:
#    - Install Supabase CLI: npm install -g supabase
#    - Run: supabase start (requires Docker)
#    - Set USE_LOCAL_SUPABASE=true
#    - Local keys are provided above (default Supabase local keys)
#
# 3. For Hybrid Setup (Recommended for Development):
#    - Set up both cloud and local configurations
#    - Toggle USE_LOCAL_SUPABASE to switch between them
#    - Use local for development, cloud for testing/staging
#
